__cs__ I discovered so many secrets .
__cs__ For example , I found if I just don &apos;t run , if I got rejected , I could actually turn a &quot; &quot; no &quot; &quot; into a &quot; &quot; yes , &quot; &quot; and the magic word is , &quot; &quot; why . &quot; &quot; So one day I went to a stranger &apos;s house , I had this flower in my hand , knocked on the door and said , &quot; Hey , can I plant this flower in your backyard ? &quot;
__cs__ ( Laughter ) And he said , &quot; &quot; No . &quot; &quot; But before he could leave I said , &quot; Hey , can I know why ? &quot;
__cs__ And he said , &quot; &quot; Well , I have this dog that would dig up anything I put in the backyard .
