__cs__ Then one day — and I also learned that I can actually say certain things and maximize my chance to get a yes .
__cs__ So for example , one day I went to a Starbucks , and asked the manager , &quot; &quot; Hey , can I be a Starbucks greeter ? &quot; &quot; He was like , &quot; &quot; What &apos;s a Starbucks greeter ? &quot; &quot; I said , &quot; &quot; Do you know those Walmart greeters ?
