__cs__ You know , I came from four generations of teachers , and my grandma has always told me , &quot; &quot; Hey Jia , you can do anything you want , but it &apos;d be great if you became a teacher . &quot; &quot; ( Laughter ) But I wanted to be an entrepreneur , so I didn &apos;t .
