__cs__ I use my blog , I use my talk , I use the book I just published , and I &apos;m even building technology to help people overcome their fear of rejection .
__cs__ When you get rejected in life , when you are facing the next obstacle or next failure , consider the possibilities .
__cs__ Don &apos;t run .
__cs__ If you just embrace them , they might become your gifts as well .
